mixin welcome
  div.splash
      h1 Collaborate on software helping further science
      p We're testing out new ways to help the research community contribute to code projects to build new tools and solve problems
  div
      div.content.content-contrast.is-center
          div.l-box-lrg.pure-u-1.pure-u-med-1-2.pure-u-lrg-1-3
              a(href="/")
                h1.content-subhead
                  i.fa.fa-link
                h3.content-subhead What we're doing
              p
                | We've curated code projects to help the research community partner together to solve problems and build new tools.
                a(href="/projects/about")  Read more about this initiative.
            div.l-box-lrg.pure-u-1.pure-u-med-1-2.pure-u-lrg-1-3
              h1.content-subhead
                i.fa.fa-users
              h3.content-subhead How you can help
              p
                | You don't need to be a scientist to get involved. There's something for designers, developers, researchers, communicators and all our contributors.
            div.l-box-lrg.pure-u-1.pure-u-med-1-2.pure-u-lrg-1-3
              h1.content-subhead
                i.fa.fa-heart
              h3.content-subhead Open & Sharing
              p
                | In the spirit of open, all projects and their outputs are openly licensed, making them easy to share and reuse with the community.



